title: Renton Rental
posting_body: ['Welcome home to this lovely 3+ bed, 2.5 Bath, with 3 car garage!', 'Step into that new construction feel with New wood floors, painted interior and trim, new carpet and bthrm floors.', 'Walk in pantry, all appls.', 'stay.', 'Fenced corner lot, prof.', 'landscaped including sprinkler system.', 'Relax and enjoy sunsets from the front porch or morning coffee on the expansive back patio.', 'The master bedroom upstairs has a 5 piece bath, WI closet and peek-a-boo view of the lake/park where trails and nature abound!', 'Get approved quickly so you can live in this beautiful home.', 'In order to qualify for the Rental Program:', '• You must have at least $85,000 in Combined Gross Household Income', '•', 'A minimum FICO score of 620', '• No evictions in the past 3 years', '• Takes 5-6 weeks from start to finish', 'We work with previous bankruptcies, foreclosures and short sales!', 'There is a 1 time $75 application fee, which is good for the whole household, and for any of our qualifying houses!', 'You must be pre-approved to view any available properties.', 'Pet Friendly!', 'Up to 3 cats/dogs OKAY!', '(Due to extreme insurance liability, we cannot allow Dobermans, Pitbulls, Rottweilers or Mastiffs)', 'Contact me today for more information and details about the program!', "The home in the picture is an example of what you could get, it's not this home in particular.", 'Kristin Hood', 'Keller Williams Lake Tapps']
